archimate:BusinessObject.name: BestEffortPackageSpec
archimate:BusinessObject.documentation:
This class defines the BestEffortService class, which provides traffic conditioning, access, and other sub-services to a set of applications that are not assigned Platinum, Gold, Silver, or Bronze Service. In other words, traffic assigned to BestEffort will not have any QoS associated with it.
Please see the DEN-ng Service model for more details.
